import numpy as np
import holoviews as hv
from holoviews import opts
from holoviews.operation.datashader import datashade, shade, dynspread, rasterize
from bokeh.models.formatters import BasicTickFormatter
hv.extension('bokeh')
In [8]:
d = pd.read_csv(
    '../simulation/random-doten.tsv',
    delimiter='\t',
    index_col='at',
    parse_dates=['at'], 
    date_parser=pd.to_datetime
)
d['bg_profit_sigma'] = d['reversal'].replace({0: d['profit_sigma'].min(), 1: d['profit_sigma'].max()})
d['bg_roc_total'] = d['reversal'].replace({0: d['roc_total'].min(), 1: d['roc_total'].max()})
d['bg_profit'] = d['reversal'].replace({0: d['profit'].min(), 1: d['profit'].max()})
d['bg_dd'] = d['reversal'].replace({0: -0.00001, 1: d['dd'].min()})

profit_sigma_bg = hv.Area(d, 'at', 'bg_profit_sigma').opts(color='#ffcccc', line_width=0, alpha=0.3, yformatter=BasicTickFormatter(use_scientific=False))
profit_sigma = hv.Curve(d, 'at', 'profit_sigma')

roc_total_bg = hv.Area(d, 'at', 'bg_roc_total').opts(color='#ffcccc', line_width=0, alpha=0.3, yformatter=BasicTickFormatter(use_scientific=False))
roc_total = hv.Curve(d, 'at', 'roc_total')

profit_bg = hv.Area(d, 'at', 'bg_profit').opts(color='#ffcccc', line_width=0, alpha=0.3, yformatter=BasicTickFormatter(use_scientific=False))
profit = hv.Spikes(d, 'at', 'profit')

dd_bg = hv.Area(d, 'at', 'bg_dd').opts(color='#ffcccc', line_width=0, alpha=0.3, yformatter=BasicTickFormatter(use_scientific=False))
dd = hv.Area(d, 'at', 'dd').opts(color='orange')

hv.Layout(profit_sigma*profit_sigma_bg + roc_total*roc_total_bg + profit*profit_bg + dd*dd_bg, label='sandbox').cols(1).opts(
    opts.Area(width=1000, xticks=10, show_grid=True),
    opts.Curve(width=1000, xticks=10, show_grid=True),
    opts.Spikes(width=1000, xticks=10, show_grid=True),
)
